text: Pregnant Kylie Jenner and her boyfriend Travis Scott have been hit with split reports just two months before her rumoured due date. The 20 - year - old Keeping Up With The Kardashians star, who is yet to publicly confirm her baby news, attended her mum Kris Jenner's annual Christmas Eve bash with her rapper beau yet just days later US sources have claimed they have broken up.
